    {
      "name": "Orders",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Order from Cart (Multiple Products)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"addressId\": 1,\n  \"couponCode\": \"BONGO10\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/order/from-cart",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "order", "from-cart"]
            },
            "description": "Place order using all cart items.\n\n🔐 REQUIRES AUTHENTICATION\n\n📋 REQUEST BODY:\n- addressId: Number (required) - must belong to logged-in user\n- couponCode: String (optional)\n\n⚠️ Do NOT send productId or items. Everything is taken from cart automatically.\n\n✅ What happens:\n1. Cart items fetched\n2. Stock checked for all products\n3. Total calculated\n4. Coupon applied (if provided)\n5. Order + OrderItems created\n6. Stock decremented\n7. Cart cleared\n\n❌ 400: Cart is empty\n❌ 400: Stock not available\n❌ 400: Invalid coupon"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Order Direct (Buy Now)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"addressId\": 1,\n  \"productId\": 5,\n  \"quantity\": 2,\n  \"couponCode\": \"BONGO10\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/order/direct",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "order", "direct"]
            },
            "description": "Place order for a single product directly (Buy Now).\n\n🔐 REQUIRES AUTHENTICATION\n\n📋 REQUEST BODY:\n- addressId: Number (required)\n- productId: Number (required)\n- quantity: Number (required)\n- couponCode: String (optional)\n\n⚠️ Cart is NOT affected.\n\n❌ 404: Product not found\n❌ 400: Stock not available\n❌ 400: Invalid coupon"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List My Orders",
